
## ‚öñÔ∏è TOS & Regulations Analyzer

The **TOS & Regulations Analyzer** is a Flask-based web application designed to quickly process and analyze lengthy legal documents like Terms of Service (TOS) and Privacy Policies using modern Machine Learning and OCR techniques.

### ‚ú® Key Features

  * **AI Summarization:** Generates a concise, abstractive summary of the legal text using a specialized Hugging Face **DistilBart model** (`ml6team/distilbart-tos-summarizer-tosdr`), making complex terms readable.
  * **Risk Assessment:** Provides a quick-view safety score and categorized risk scores (e.g., Privacy, User Rights) based on analysis heuristics.
  * **Aggressive Language & Clauses:** Highlights suspicious wording and problematic clauses detected in the text.
  * **Optical Character Recognition (OCR):** Allows users to input text by uploading an image or taking a photo (via a webcam) using **Tesseract** to extract the text.

